The modern fashion-conscious woman is marked by her self-confidence and outspoken nature and what better way to showcase yours than this trendy printed tee from the house of Tantra? The brash-yet-cool message on the chest of this half sleeved T-shirt speaks volumes about your self-assured nature without looking too arrogant. Made from soft 100 per cent cotton
column13:
this yellow T-shirt keeps you ultra-comfy and feeling pristine when weekend is round the corner.

Go edgy and team the Tantra T-shirt with turquoise blue jeggings and a sporty pair of sneakers. Throw on a sling bag or a knit jacket and look stellar.
